S. V. Ray, Administrator of the Estate of Eugenia G. McRee, and the Fidelity and Deposit Company of Maryland, a Corporation, Plaintiffs in Error, v. Park Trammell, Governor of the State of Florida for the use and benefit of Jules McRee, an infant, Defendant in Error. A wrijt of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Hillsborough. Lucas & Withers, for Plaintiff in Error; Dickenson & Dickenson, for Defendant in Error.

Writ 'of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.
